Title: systemd_services: Extension of services classification functionality
Level: 2
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 2.0.0i1
Date: 1563283599
Class: feature

The systemd services summary check plugin obtains the functionality to assess static and activating processes in a separate batch. Regarding the activating services, a new WATO rule has been implemented which allows to specify "lenient" time periods.
